An emergency call was received by the Middelburg Dagpatrollie group earlier and authorities are on the lookout for a white Toyota double cab bakkie containing four suspects armed with AK 47 rifles. Police have responded to the scene and are in pursuit of the suspected vehicle. The vehicle description received is as follows:
The white Toyota is a 4X4 double cab with a silver bull bar. It only contains a front registration plate. Anyone who sights the vehicle is asked to inform Middelburg Dagpatrollie members on 083 870 9693.